latestIgtvVideos.caption:
After spending several years trying to distance herself from her childhood and her father, Kia is forced to return. Her father is in a critical condition and could pass away any second; her sister and her mother insist that her last words to him should be a fond goodbye. Kia has to decide what her last few words to her father will be. 🎈🐾

latestPosts.caption:
A little self-care moment for the most low-maintenance man I know. 💌
Took Dad on a surprise @sephora_india run for Father’s Day and let him explore everything from grooming to fragrance.

One thing’s for sure, we’re surely doing this trip again! 

Shop now in-store, at sephora.in or on the Sephora app.

What. A. Finale. 💥

After a nail-biting clash against the mighty @sobomumbaifalcons led by the dynamic @shreyasiyer96 , the @maratharoyalsofficial rise as the champions of the @t20mumbai League — and what a well-deserved win it was! 🏆🔥

Led brilliantly by my dear friend and captain, the calm and composed @ladsid this victory was long-awaited and oh-so-sweet. Watching Sid lift that trophy with @hirokhatri by his side… my heart is full. 🧡

Five years later, the Royals reclaim their throne — and I couldn’t be prouder. The boys played their best match yet!! 

It’s a wrap on T20 Mumbai League for me and my partner @apurvasinghrathore @sau_100_rab at @workingpandafilms — and what a journey it’s been. 🏏🎬

A special thank you to @aj.naik and @vihangpratap @mumbaicricassoc for this absolutely wonderful and life changing opportunity! This is just the beginning of a storm were about to cook up! 🐼🏏❤️👯‍♀️🏆

latestPosts.caption:
🎤 Had the absolute honour of interviewing Sarpanch Sahab himself — @shreyasiyer96 , the dynamic captain of the @sobomumbaifalcons for the @t20mumbai League . 🏏

From leading @kkriders to a title win in 2024 and having captained @punjabkingsipl in the 2025 in the @iplt20 and India A before that, Shreyas has been wearing the captain’s hat since he was just 22. Leadership runs in his blood, and his calm, composed energy is just magnetic.

At only 30, he’s already a seasoned leader with a world of wisdom. Listening to him share his journey was inspiring beyond words — the future is blazing bright for this phenomenal cricketer. 🌟
